---
import LinkJob from "./icons/LinkJob.astro";
---

<ol class="relative border-s border-gray-700 dark:border-gray-200">                  
    <li class="mb-10 ms-2 md:ms-8">
        <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-black dark:bg-white rounded-full -start-3 ring-8 ring-gray-50 dark:ring-[#09101b]">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white dark:text-[#09101b]" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
            </svg>
        </span>
        <div class="bg-slate-300/45 dark:bg-[#ffffff1c] md:bg-transparent md:hover:bg-slate-300/45 dark:md:hover:bg-[#ffffff1c] rounded-2xl p-6 transition-colors duration-500 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" id="card1">
            <h3 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold dark:text-white duration-500"> Web Developer </h3>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/zapata-camiones-s-a-de-c-v-/posts/?feedView=all" target="_blank" class="flex w-fit">
                <h2 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl text-black dark:text-white group duration-500"> Zapata
                    <LinkJob class="size-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
                </h2>
            </a>
            <time class="block my-2 mb-4 text-sm md:text-base font-normal leading-none text-[#e74d3c]"> November 2024 - Currently </time>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg font-normal opacity-80">
                I'm responsible for maintaining and improving the company's websites, development with Laravel, Bootstrap and JavaScript. I actively participate in the development of new features and database management.
            </p>
            <h3 class="md:text-lg">Responsibilities and Activities:</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 mx-8 list-disc opacity-80 md:text-lg">
                <li> Develop new modules and functions for the websites, including the desing deployment and integration of business logic. </li>
                <li> Handle debugging, optimization and database management to ensure data integrity and efficiency. </li>
                <li> Website content management and upadates. </li>
                <li> Detection and correction of errors implementing robust solutions to ensure scalability and efficiency. </li>
                <li> Improvement website performance and security. </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-4 mb-10 ms-2 md:ms-8">            
        <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 bg-black dark:bg-white rounded-full -start-3 ring-8 ring-gray-50 dark:ring-[#09101b]">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white dark:text-[#09101b]" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
            </svg>
        </span>
        <div class="bg-slate-300/45 dark:bg-[#ffffff1c] md:bg-transparent md:hover:bg-slate-300/45 dark:md:hover:bg-[#ffffff1c] rounded-2xl p-6 transition text-gray-800 dark:text-white" id="card2">
            <h3 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold"> Software Developer </h3>
            <a href="https://barcostudio.com/" target="_blank" class="flex w-fit">
                <h2 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl group"> Barcostudio Agencia Tecnológica
                    <LinkJob class="size-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" />
                </h2>
            </a>
            <time class="block my-2 mb-4 text-sm md:text-base font-normal leading-none text-[#e74d3c]"> August 2023 - October 2024 </time>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg font-normal opacity-80">
                During my experience as software developer, I actively participate in all stages of the web application development life cylce, using technologies such as Laravel, Bootstrap and JavaScript. I developed and deployed RESTful APIs using .NET ensuring efficient integration that enabled the develoment of solid and scalable systems. I managed databases and created technical documentation.
            </p>
            <h3 class=" md:text-lg"> Responsabilities and Activities: </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 mx-8 md:text-lg list-disc opacity-80">
                <li> Interface layout design for web application using HTML5, CSS, Bootstrap and JavaScript, ensuring a fully responsive design starting from mockups.</li>
                <li> Development of business logic on the backend using Laravel following MVC pattern, with custom feature implementation based on application-specific requirements. </li>
                <li> Design, development and deployment of RESTfuk APIs using C# and .NET. </li>
                <li> Administration and maintaining of databases using SQL Server and MySQL. </li>
                <li> Teamwork following scrum methodology, actively collaborating with the team to archieve goals.</li>
                <li> Creating technical documentation, explaining the use of features for maintenance and future updates. </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-4 ms-2 md:ms-8">            
        <span class="absolute flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6  bg-black dark:bg-white rounded-full -start-3 ring-8 ring-gray-50 dark:ring-[#09101b]">
            <svg class="w-2.5 h-2.5 text-white dark:text-[#09101b]" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path d="M20 4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-2V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1h-3V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H6V1a1 1 0 0 0-2 0v1H2a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v2h20V4ZM0 18a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8H0v10Zm5-8h10a1 1 0 0 1 0 2H5a1 1 0 0 1 0-2Z"/>
            </svg>
        </span>
        <div class="bg-slate-300/45 dark:bg-[#ffffff1c] md:bg-transparent md:hover:bg-slate-300/45 dark:md:hover:bg-[#ffffff1c] rounded-2xl p-6 transition text-gray-800 dark:text-white" id="card3">
            <h3 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold"> Trainee </h3>
            <a href="https://barcostudio.com/" target="_blank" class="flex w-fit">
                <h2 class="flex items-center text-lg md:text-xl group"> Barcostudio Agencia Tecnológica
                    <LinkJob class="size-4 group-hover:-translate-y-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-all" />
                </h2>
            </a>
            <time class="block my-2 mb-4 text-sm md:text-base font-normal leading-none text-[#e74d3c]"> Febrero 2023 - August 2023 </time>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base md:text-lg font-normal opacity-80">
                In my role as a Trainee, I was part of the web development team where I was involved in various tasks, contributing to interface designs and supporting web application development.
            </p>
            <h3 class="md:text-lg"> Responsabilities and Activities: </h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 mx-8 md:text-lg list-disc opacity-80">
                <li> Interface layout design for website and web applications using HTML5, CSS and Bootstrap. </li>
                <li> Design and development of storage procedures. </li>
                <li> Execution of unit tests for error detection. </li>
                <li> Internal training on tools and technologies for software development. </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </li>
</ol>